			</div>			<div id="post-696" class="post-696 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-uncategorized" itemprop="blogPosts" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/BlogPosting">
				<h2 class="posttitle"><a href="http://ottopress.com/2011/migrated-to-dreamhost/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Migrated to DreamHost" itemprop="url"><span itemprop="name">Migrated to DreamHost</span></a></h2>
				<div class="postmetadata">October 11, 2011, 7:42 pm <!-- by <span rel="author">Samuel “Otto” Wood</span> --></div>
				<div class="postentry" itemprop="description">
					<p>If you&#8217;re seeing this, then my site has been migrated to DreamHost.</p>
<p>Note that while I set things up, I fully expect the site to break from time to time. So&#8230; gimme time to get it working properly.</p>
